{"title":"伪装的杀手（图片）","authors":["徐鹏飞","池北偶"],"dates":[{"year":1999,"month":5,"day":21}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"伪装的杀手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"徐鹏飞画  池北偶诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和平鸽般装扮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"筑巢基地、航舰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘴叼橄榄树枝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竟是巡航导弹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"君临山峦小国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"作恶却称行善。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"专门从事“误炸”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"靶子就在民间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"武器绝顶精确，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当然不会炸偏。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"既炸学校、民房，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也炸医院、电站；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炸了难民车队，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又炸中国使馆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滥杀无辜平民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"制造血腥灾难，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手段实在残忍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"行径极端野蛮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"口口声声“人权”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地地道道战犯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狡辩纯属白搭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难逃历史审判。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}